name: Varsity Cornhole
description:
Maybe you can't play football, or baseball or basketball. But if there were a varsity team for the backyard sport of cornhole, you would be on it! For those who aren't familiar with cornhole (also known as bean bag toss), it is a game played across the midwest at barbeques, picnics and tailgate parties. It is one for those games that is best played while drinking a cold beer, and entails throwing a corn filled bag through a hole in a board, kinda like skeeball meets bocce ball.

My original design screenprinted with non-toxic water based red ink on a gray shirt. Available in mens/unisex shirt in S, M, L or XL.
